          , Pu = "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789+/=";
        var Tu = {
            encode: function(e) {
                for (var t, n, r, o, i, a, s, c = "", l = 0, u = function(e) {
                    var t = e;
                    t = t.replace(/\r\n/g, "\n");
                    for (var n = "", r = 0; r < t.length; r++) {
                        var o = t.charCodeAt(r);
                        o < 127 ? n += String.fromCharCode(o) : o > 127 && o < 2048 ? (n += String.fromCharCode(o >> 6 | 192),
                        n += String.fromCharCode(63 & o | 128)) : (n += String.fromCharCode(o >> 12 | 224),
                        n += String.fromCharCode(o >> 6 & 63 | 128),
                        n += String.fromCharCode(63 & o | 128))
                    }
                    return n
                }(e); l < u.length; )
                    o = (t = u.charCodeAt(l++)) >> 2,
                    i = (3 & t) << 4 | (n = u.charCodeAt(l++)) >> 4,
                    a = (15 & n) << 2 | (r = u.charCodeAt(l++)) >> 6,
                    s = 63 & r,
                    isNaN(n) ? (a = 64,
                    s = 64) : isNaN(r) && (s = 64),
                    c = c + Pu.charAt(o) + Pu.charAt(i) + Pu.charAt(a) + Pu.charAt(s);
                return c
            },
